HEADWORD: Rensselaerite
<hw>Rens"se*laer*ite</hw> <pr>(r?ns"s<it>e</it>-l?r-?t)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>A soft, compact variety of talc,,
